{"url": "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_program.php?catoid=11&poid=10488&returnto=3756", "type": "program", "title": "Program: Game Audio Minor - University of Southern California - Acalog ACMS\u2122", "description": "To implement audio into a game requires an understanding that audio forms one part of a game system or algorithm, and even composition must often be thought of in terms of programming-like logic. Game audio professionals must not only be competent in one area (e.g., expressly in music composing, or in audio recording), but in other areas of audio as well. This minor provides a grounding in game design and systems thinking, while providing a theoretical backing and skills in audio design and composition to prepare students to design successful audio for the games industry.", "course": ["https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161057", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=168926", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161066", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161067", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161081", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161084", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161077", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161078", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161080", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161082", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161085", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161086", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=161159", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=168921", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=168922", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=168940", "https://catalogue.usc.edu/preview_course.php?catoid=11&coid=168943